author: MZ_1
title: Wu is back!
review:
I found it by accident on a kiosk shelf.

Packaging / Instructions
The minifigure is packed in a foil bag with glue stronger than before. In the magazine, surprisingly, there was an instruction! It wasn't needed, but it is.

Minifigures
For that matter, the Young Wu minifigure is the highlight of the set. He has Cole's hair from Ninjago Movie repainted, an exclusive head and torso to this character, and plain, unprinted black legs.

Parts
Nothing interesting. We get 2 golden lightsaber handles, a brown 3L stick and 2 small white fangs.

Generally
It is a great set, mainly because of the minifigure and the low price.
